This is written to address
http://perlmonks.org/?node_id=670068


The package View::bullet::text requires HTML::Format which is kind of
hard to install via CPAN... do this:


cpan> i S/SB/SBURKE/HTML-Format-2.04.tar.gz
Distribution id = S/SB/SBURKE/HTML-Format-2.04.tar.gz

cpan> install S/SB/SBURKE/HTML-Format-2.04.tar.gz

